> >   I've got no indication in the logs that something went wrong, nor
> > do I see any kernel BUG or WARNING.
> > 
> >   My box is a dual 2.8GHz HT xeon w/ 2GB mem.
> > 
> >   rt29 was fine as is 2.6.17-rc6.
> > 
> >   I feel a bit perplexed here.
